{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-10","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Lekcija 10","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Otro</span> (muški) na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">otra</span> (ženski) koristi se za razgovor o nečemu drugom ili drugačijem. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Quiero otro café.</span> – Želim još jednu kafu. (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">Café</span> je muški rod, zato se <span class=\"highlighted-text\">otro</span> koristi ovde).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Necesito otra copia.</span> – Trebam još jednu kopiju. (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">Copia</span> je žensko, zato se <span class=\"highlighted-text\">otra</span> koristi ovde).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Kada potvrđuješ stvari, često ćeš čuti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">otra</span> pomešan sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">vez</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Vez</span> znači događaj ili trenutak kada se nešto dogodi. To je ženski imenica. Jer je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">vez</span> žensko, ovaj izraz uvek koristi ženski rod:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Puedes repetirlo otra vez?</span> - Možete li ponoviti?</p>\n<p>Ovaj uobičajen izraz koristi se za govor o radnji više puta ili ponovnom činu.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio i dovršite rečenice ispod.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Otra vez</span> meša:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Otra</span> (ženski tip za „ostale“).</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Vez</span> (vreme / događaj).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pošto je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">vez</span> žensko, uvek koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">otra vez</span>.</p>\n<p>Puna fraza se često koristi za zahtev ili ukazivanje na to da nešto mora da se ponovi.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-10"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>¿BLANK BLANK, por favor?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Otra","feedback":"<p>Ova reč se koristi za govor o nečemu drugom ili drugačijem.</p>"},{"answer":"vez","feedback":"<p>Ova imenica se odnosi na događaj ili vreme kada nešto nastaje.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room2.png","characters":[{"character":"Camila","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_mateo_camila_phone_number_dialogue.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":41.19,"finishTimestamp":43},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Camila","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Camila","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.8,"dialogue":{"text":"¿Otra vez, por favor?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Camila","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.95,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","dashedName":"task-10","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-basic-personal-details","module":"es-a1-module-sharing-your-personal-details","block":"es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastCha